  "description": "The Cinderwrit Stock Vault serves as the Exchange’s sealed storage chamber, its basalt-and-slagcrete walls lined with ceramite-faced shelves and lockable crate racks. A pressure door with ash-gasket seals isolates the room from Ashenward City’s grit-laden drafts, leaving a persistent mineral dryness in the air. Lumen strips recessed behind wire guards cast hard, clinical light over inventory tags and stamped lot marks. The floor matches the shop’s vitrified paving, its violet sheen interrupted by scuffed drag-lines where cargo is staged and turned.",
